Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:52.93,Main,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Our king certainly was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:53.91,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Several Kings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:58.74,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,Ensho falls in the battle with Takasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:58.74,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,What words does Nobunobu \Ngive the soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:04.25,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,And it's been a long time coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:04.25,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,but these sisters make their comebacks, too!